Package: distfitr
Type: Package
Title: Statistical Distribution Fitting and Goodness-of-Fit Testing
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Ali", "Sadeghi Aghili",
           email = "alisadeghiaghili@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5938-3291"))
    )
Maintainer: Ali Sadeghi Aghili <alisadeghiaghili@gmail.com>
Description: A toolkit for fitting probability distributions to data using
    Maximum Likelihood Estimation (MLE), Method of Moments (MME), and
    Quantile Matching Estimation (QME). Provides goodness-of-fit tests
    (Kolmogorov-Smirnov, Anderson-Darling, Chi-Square, Cramer-von Mises),
    distribution diagnostics (residuals, influence measures, outlier
    detection), bootstrap confidence intervals (parametric, non-parametric,
    and BCa), and multilingual output (English, Persian/Farsi, German).
